<style>
  :host {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    width: 100%;
    min-width: 320px;
    max-width: 640px;
    height: 64px;
    pointer-events: auto;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0 24px;
    align-items: center;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  [public] {
    --svg-icon-color: #4caf50;
  }

  .flex {
    flex: 1;
  }
  .filler {
    display: block;
    min-width: 240px;
  }
  input {
    width: 100px;
  }
  h4, p, span {
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .row {
    width: 100%;
  }
  apply(--css-row)
  apply(--css-center)
</style>

<span class="row center">
  <h4 class="name center">
